  <section id="eip-124"><title>Element of Economics</title><para id="eip-744"><title>Prices bring the choices of buyers and sellers into balance. </title></para></section><section id="eip-544"><title>Video</title><para id="eip-680"><figure id="moonlanding-youtube"><media id="yt-media" display="block" alt="Short lecture">
